<footer class="w-full" style="background-color: #07070D; border-top: 2px solid #9b5fe0; box-shadow: 0 -10px 30px rgba(155,95,224,0.15);">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 px-6 py-12 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<!-- Brand Column -->
<div class="space-y-6">
<span class="text-3xl font-black font-orbitron uppercase" style="color: #9b5fe0;">AbigBoysGame</span>
<p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #acaab1;">
                    De ultieme bestemming voor retro gamers. Tweedehands & Nieuw — uitvoerig getest, met passie geselecteerd.
                </p>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<a class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm transition-colors duration-300 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100" style="background-color: #25252d; color: #acaab1;" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">share</span>
</a>
<a class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm transition-colors duration-300 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100" style="background-color: #25252d; color: #acaab1;" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">rss_feed</span>
</a>
<a class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm transition-colors duration-300 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100" style="background-color: #25252d; color: #acaab1;" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">public</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Links Column 1 -->
<div>
<h4 class="font-headline font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #9b5fe0;">Klantenservice</h4>
<ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-body" style="color: #acaab1;">
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">Contact opnemen</a></li>
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">Veelgestelde vragen</a></li>
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">Verzendbeleid</a></li>
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">Garantie &amp; Kwaliteitscontrole</a></li>

</ul>
</div>
<!-- Links Column 2 -->
<div>
<h4 class="font-headline font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #9b5fe0;">Populaire Categorieën</h4>
<ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-body" style="color: #acaab1;">
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">Nintendo consoles</a></li>
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">PlayStation games</a></li>
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">Sega verzamelaarsobjecten</a></li>
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="#">Retro hardware</a></li>
<li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 font-bold" style="color: #9b5fe0;" href="#">Weekdeals</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Newsletter Column -->
<div>
<h4 class="font-headline font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #9b5fe0;">Nieuwsbrief</h4>
<p class="text-sm font-body mb-6" style="color: #acaab1;">Meld je aan voor exclusieve drops en retro nieuws.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
<input class="px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none transition-all" style="background: #000000; border: 1px solid rgba(72,71,77,0.3); color: #f9f5fd;" placeholder="E-mailadres" type="email"/>
<button class="py-3 font-orbitron font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:brightness-110 transition-all" style="background: #9b5fe0; color: #ffffff;">Inschrijven</button>
</div>
